<TEXT>
<P>
Crescenta Valley 9, Burroughs 5 -- Damon Martin kicked field goals of 43, 30 
and 31 yards as Crescenta Valley won at Burroughs. Burroughs (1-4) had a chance 
to win the game on its final possession, driving to Crescenta Valley's 19-yard 
line, but John Rogers intercepted tailback Danny Suarez's pass in the end zone. 
</P>
<P>
Jeff Gierok kicked a 27-yard second-quarter field goal, and Martin conceded a 
safety in the fourth quarter, accounting for Burroughs' scoring. 
</P>
<P>
Crescenta Valley's Colby Bogust rushed for a game-high 73 yards in 10 carries 
as the Falcons (4-1) gained 162 of their 193 yards on the ground. 
</P>
<P>
Burroughs quarterback Dennis Rodriguez completed seven of 10 passes for 55 
yards, 54 in the first half. MIKE GLAZE 
