<LENGTH>
<P>
81 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY DIGEST: FULLERTON; 
</P>
<P>
SPORTS ALLIANCE DONATES $3,000 TO JUNIOR HIGHS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Fullerton Athletic Alliance, an organization that raises funds to assist 
the Fullerton School District's after-school sports program, has donated $3,000 
to help Fullerton's three junior high schools participate in the North Orange 
County Athletic League. 
</P>
<P>
John Charlton, director of the league, said the money will be used to purchase 
uniforms, soccer nets, paint to mark fields and chalk for the track fields at 
Nicolas, D. Russell Parks and Ladera Vista junior high schools. 
</P>
</TEXT>
