<HEADLINE>
<P>
LOS ALAMITOS BLASTS LAKEWOOD TO IMPROVE TO 4-1 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LAKEWOOD 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Quarterback Todd Gragnano completed 10 of 21 pass attempts for 298 yards and 
three touchdowns as Los Alamitos High School rolled to a 35-7 victory Friday 
night over host Lakewood. 
</P>
<P>
Running back Erik Mitchell rushed for 65 yards and two touchdowns and had 115 
yards and another touchdown in pass receptions as Los Alamitos improved to 4-1. 
Lakewood is 1-4. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Game Story 
